{"tid":123823,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[I/A] 遊戲王Duel Links [10] 衝定stage 等打盃","createTime":"2017-02-17T06:13:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-23T08:52:32.000Z","uid":3163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"351997e7ae3eac87286f8206877816baf1d7c894","tid":123823,"uid":3163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T06:13:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">洗唔洗刷首抽</span><br />\n唔洗，個box啲卡限死數量，終有一日會抽晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">點解個場得三格/點解deck限20-30張卡</span><br />\n本遊戲採取快速決鬥規則<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">點拎角色</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://news.isheart.com/archives/4433\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.isheart.com%2Farchives%2F4433&d=7EcP4%2BvGpl6inSsjOqiUXqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=5a389ffd\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.isheart.com/archives/4433</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">啲卡點拎</span><br />\n分別有<br />\n角色等級獎勵<br />\n卡片商人 (stage7 unlock)<br />\n路人掉落<br />\n打Gate<br />\n同埋抽卡包<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">咩叫Reset 卡包</span><br />\n抽完/抽中目標物之後 可以reset卡包重頭抽過<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">新手抽邊個卡包好</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n普遍巴打認為抽1/2先<br />\n1泛用性高 2主題deck而且易組 <br />\n3啲卡都勁，但冇咁易組deck<br />\n15/2 卡包1&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;2將會下架<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">點set技能</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/13/110027_99ac597844832fc8b37f05deb821e538.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F13%2F110027_99ac597844832fc8b37f05deb821e538.jpg&h=325aa7f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Quiz點打</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/G2.php?bsn=29618&amp;amp;amp;sn=108\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FG2.php%3Fbsn%3D29618%26amp%3Bamp%3Bsn%3D108&d=7EcP4%2BvGpl6inSsjOqiUXqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=4951bfb3\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/G2.php?bsn=29618&amp;amp;amp;sn=108</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">打Gate有咩要注意</span><br />\n除左解任之外儲key先<br />\n等到unlock lv40先去刷卡刷技<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">結算分點計</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/u2dtrpnz\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fu2dtrpnz&h=6c55a497&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">點樣刷到高分</span><br />\n魔導獸deck<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/shared?ci=J5cN0TBKmWE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fshared%3Fci%3DJ5cN0TBKmWE&d=7EcP4%2BvGpl6inSsjOqiUXqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=8f223f38\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/shared?ci=J5cN0TBKmWE</a><br />\n打法係堆攻擊力過一萬同壓血<br />\n（其實一隻魔導獸都得）<br />\n<br />\n刷海馬lv40 deck<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/shared?ci=Tir-2A-gu6Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fshared%3Fci%3DTir-2A-gu6Y&d=7EcP4%2BvGpl6inSsjOqiUXqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=0239b15b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/shared?ci=Tir-2A-gu6Y</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">咩叫派小智/流浪者/神秘人/紅帽 etc</span><br />\n係你加左好友之後<br />\n有時打完佢會問你有冇朋友介紹，同埋要set咩challenge 俾佢<br />\n揀一張卡起手就啱架啦，超過二千經驗值<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">免費石呀！！！</span></span><br />\n點觸遊戲介面以下地方可獲得數量1、3、5顆不等的石頭。<br />\n1.噴水池：出現噴水彩虹<br />\n2.街燈：發出彩虹光<br />\n3.商店上方卡片：出現禮物汽球<br />\n4.垃圾桶：出現強慾之壺<br />\n獲得一定時間過後可再次點觸獲得。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">參考兼攻略網</span><br />\n英文<a href=\"http://duellinks.gamea.co/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fduellinks.gamea.co%2F&d=7EcP4%2BvGpl6inSsjOqiUXqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=2dc90230\" target=\"_blank\">http://duellinks.gamea.co/</a><br />\n日文<a href=\"https://duellinks.gamewith.jp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fduellinks.gamewith.jp%2F&d=7EcP4%2BvGpl6inSsjOqiUXqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=87ddfcb6\" target=\"_blank\">https://duellinks.gamewith.jp/</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"0f26e0dba6f38cbe613db665dc4fe1f0fe36a89d","tid":123823,"uid":3163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T06:14:47.000Z","msg":"有無人貼番個template link <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cccb93198ddd53e8123154542aa5bbe3be5a970","tid":123823,"uid":75012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T07:11:55.000Z","msg":"新手Lm"},{"pid":"820f9b9059e36df1a62d1b17de9fc998b27505f9","tid":123823,"uid":45944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T07:45:31.000Z","msg":"搞乜無哂人"},{"pid":"dab64c336b976e23b0f97dff3c67912797bd8393","tid":123823,"uid":49430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T08:52:32.000Z","msg":"招好友 留名 火球鼠 228-687-159<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}